What is the projected market size & growth rate of the Endocrine Disorders Market?

Market Analysis and Size

The global endocrine disorders market is expected to witness significant growth during the forecast period. The rising diabetic, geriatric, and obese population globally is expected to promote market growth. Advancements in technologies such as the introduction of easy-to-operate test kits facilitated the penetration of home-based diagnosis, which is user-friendly and cost-effective. As per the International Federation, in 2021, around 537 million adults were living with diabetes, and by 2045, this number will increase to 783 million. Increasing diabetes worldwide will lead to increase adoption of insulin hormone testing, thereby projected to boost the market growth.

